reviews.title: Severe bug
reviews.comment: I think I have discovered a severe bug in the shake games I have played so far. In tap mode, when there are times we got to tap both notes simultaneously and the note at right needs to slide to other notes later, the tap at the right will be freezed from sliding to other notes, causing irritating undeserving misses and I think many people will reguard this as lag.

reviews.title: IOS to Android ver
reviews.comment: I have 5 shake games which used to work flawlessly on my ipod touch but after changing to S3, I start to experience slight lag in between notes sliding. But that\'s still bearable except for Girl\'s Generation Shake. Sadly that\'s my most played game but now the notes lags too much just like back when the game first released in playstore which really spoils the fun. I guess that might be why it\'s removed from store. I was only able to download gg shake through account history.
